if it kills me.

33:08.943 --> 33:10.945
Oh.

33:21.564 --> 33:24.480
I'm sorry. You were right.

33:24.524 --> 33:27.266
"All adventures
together, forever,

33:27.309 --> 33:29.311
even when we're old and fat."

33:31.487 --> 33:33.533
Oh, oh.

33:38.625 --> 33:40.627
Let's just go home.

33:50.854 --> 33:53.553
♪ Hey, now

33:53.596 --> 33:57.252
