33:57.296 --> 34:02.431
♪ But stay now

34:02.475 --> 34:05.086
♪ Things just starting
getting good and ♪

34:05.130 --> 34:06.609
Another, please.

34:06.653 --> 34:10.657
Of course.♪ Don't you let me walk away

34:12.920 --> 34:16.054
♪ You'd be begging me
to stay ♪

34:16.097 --> 34:17.316
Here you are, sir.

34:17.359 --> 34:20.014
Thank you.
You're welcome.

34:20.058 --> 34:25.063
♪ You'd be calling out my name

34:25.106 --> 34:27.848
There you are.

34:27.891 --> 34:32.853
♪ Oh, calling out my name...

34:32.896 --> 34:35.029
There's someone waiting
for Mr. Carrington in the study.

34:35.073 --> 34:36.074
Thank you.

34:36.117 --> 34:39.512
♪ Whoa, calling out my name...

34:39.555 --> 34:41.209
Cristal. What are
you doing here?

34:41.253 --> 34:43.472
I heard you might need me.

34:46.954 --> 34:48.521
Look, I did what you wanted.

34:48.564 --> 34:50.914
You nearly blew my operation
attempting to rescue Jeff Colby.

34:50.958 --> 34:51.915
You and I are done.

34:51.959 --> 34:52.960
ADA:
Really?

34:53.003 --> 34:54.701
You just broke the law.

34:54.744 --> 34:56.790
You should be grateful I even
gave you time to escape.

34:56.833 --> 34:58.879
Yeah, well, what if I go
to the Feds about you?

34:58.922 --> 35:01.055
That will require you knowing
how to find me.

35:01.099 --> 35:02.491
I'm like a ghost.

35:02.535 --> 35:03.884
In Gucci.

35:03.927 --> 35:05.538
Well, I'm leaving Atlanta.

35:05.581 --> 35:08.018
For that New York job
you've been mooning over?

35:08.062 --> 35:10.630
W What

35:10.673 --> 35:11.848
I was listening in on the mic

35:11.892 --> 35:13.241
when you were talking to Fallon,
silly.

35:13.285 --> 35:16.940
I made a call to a friend
in a very high place,

35:16.984 --> 35:19.334
and kind of took you
out of the running.

35:19.378 --> 35:21.031
Sorry, Michael.

35:21.075 --> 35:23.991
You work for me now,
and you're going all in.

35:25.253 --> 35:26.559
WOMAN:
Ms. Carrington?

35:26.602 --> 35:27.864
FALLON:
Yes?

35:27.908 --> 35:28.865
You have a call.

35:28.909 --> 35:30.519
Oh. Thank you.

35:32.652 --> 35:34.088
Hello?

35:34.132 --> 35:36.917
Was Paraguay the family vacation
you'd hoped for?

35:36.960 --> 35:37.874
What do you want, Kirby?

35:37.918 --> 35:39.354
Well, I didn't see any photos.

35:39.398 --> 35:42.183
You know, people love to share
every minor details

35:42.227 --> 35:44.446
of their travels these days.
"Look at me!"

35:44.490 --> 35:47.667
"Look at my new bag!"
"I'm rich!" It's sick.

35:47.710 --> 35:49.059
You little bitch.

35:49.103 --> 35:50.844
You're the one
that set me up.

35:50.887 --> 35:53.673
Do you have any idea of
the destruction that you caused?

35:53.716 --> 35:55.892
No, but I was hoping.

35:55.936 --> 35:59.287
This sounds like a challenge,
and I adore a challenge.

35:59.331 --> 36:01.985
I got rid of you once before,
and I'll do it again.

36:02.029 --> 36:03.552
FALLON:
It was a disaster,

36:03.596 --> 36:06.381
and then we built a house, and
then it was a disaster again.

36:06.425 --> 36:07.600
There. You're all caught up.

36:07.643 --> 36:09.950
Well,
I'm sorry I missed it.

36:09.993 --> 36:11.125
Mmm.

36:12.866 --> 36:15.521
Well, it turns out I
could have been there.

36:15.564 --> 36:16.739
I didn't get the job.

36:16.783 --> 36:18.785
What? No!

36:18.828 --> 36:20.308
I'm sorry.

36:20.352 --> 36:21.744
I can make some calls.

36:21.788 --> 36:23.398
I'll have meetings
set up by tomorrow.

36:23.442 --> 36:25.226
Oh, no, no, no,
that's okay.

36:25.270 --> 36:27.141
I don't want to force it.

36:27.185 --> 36:30.927
I got to accept some things
are just out of my control.

36:33.016 --> 36:37.151
I heard about everything
that happened, your son.

36:37.195 --> 36:38.805
Mm.

36:38.848 --> 36:40.589
I'm so sorry, Blake.

36:41.634 --> 36:43.157
You're strong.

36:43.201 --> 36:45.290
Strong people have
a hard time

36:45.333 --> 36:47.335
accepting help
when it's offered.

36:47.379 --> 36:48.945
Celia was like that?

36:48.989 --> 36:50.817
Yeah, she could be stubborn.

36:50.860 --> 36:52.949
It's part of why we were
attracted to each other.

36:52.993 --> 36:55.604
If it wasn't for you,
I never would have met her,

36:55.648 --> 36:57.432
and then I never
would have met you.

36:57.476 --> 37:02.568
I... feel fate
brought me back here.

37:02.611 --> 37:05.048
Yeah, maybe the first time,

37:05.092 --> 37:08.965
but I'm not convinced it was
fate that brought you back.

37:13.361 --> 37:14.710
Did you call Cristal?

37:16.756 --> 37:19.280
Sir, please.
