a saint back then.

37:35.209 --> 37:37.298
I did my fair
share of cheating.

37:37.342 --> 37:41.781
It was a difficult time, and
I'm pleased we had this talk.

37:41.824 --> 37:44.087
But I'm all packed,
ready to hit the road.

37:44.131 --> 37:46.525
You're not going anywhere.

37:46.568 --> 37:49.354
And we have a son together now.

37:49.397 --> 37:52.095
I think we make a
pretty good team.

37:52.139 --> 37:53.575
Names aren't what make a family.

37:55.273 --> 37:56.926
People do.

37:56.970 --> 38:00.887
STEVEN:
♪ The thrill
of being sheltered ♪

38:00.930 --> 38:04.412
♪ In your arms

38:04.456 --> 38:08.982
♪ Of course I do

38:09.025 --> 38:18.034
♪ But I get along
without you very well... ♪

38:18.078 --> 38:20.210
