38:20.254 --> 38:22.474
Yeah. I'm always
accompanying you.

38:24.214 --> 38:27.087
Can't sleep?
I guess I miss
that polyester sack.

38:27.130 --> 38:29.132
You mean a
sleeping bag?

38:29.176 --> 38:30.699
Yeah, sure. Whatever.

38:30.743 --> 38:32.397
Anders was right.

38:32.440 --> 38:35.487
The only thing that trip proved
was that you are the glue

38:35.530 --> 38:37.315
that holds everyone
in this family together.

38:37.358 --> 38:39.273
That trip proved that
this family should stick

38:39.317 --> 38:42.102
to building dynasties,
not houses.

38:42.145 --> 38:46.019
Not you. You could do anything.

38:46.062 --> 38:49.065
And instead, you do everything
for everyone else.

38:50.415 --> 38:52.242
And you can't do it anymore.

38:52.286 --> 38:54.375
I won't let you.

38:54.419 --> 38:55.724
Fallon.

38:58.118 --> 39:00.120
You need to go.

39:01.861 --> 39:03.384
I don't want you to,

39:03.428 --> 39:05.821
but you know
it's what you have to do.

39:07.823 --> 39:10.260
Okay, please, can you say
something before I take it back?

39:10.304 --> 39:12.567
Thank you, Fallon.

39:12.611 --> 39:15.178
You are the strongest
person I know.

39:16.789 --> 39:18.617
You don't need anyone,
certainly not me.

39:18.660 --> 39:21.620
I hope you know that.

39:21.663 --> 39:24.100
While you're in
a generous mood,

39:24.144 --> 39:27.016
there's something else
I need you to do.
What?

39:27.060 --> 39:28.191
Reconcile with Mom.

39:28.235 --> 39:31.020
No, no. I'd rather
build an entire village.

39:31.064 --> 39:33.022
I know. Please.

39:33.066 --> 39:35.373
For me.

39:36.156 --> 39:38.288
Okay, sure.

39:38.332 --> 39:40.247
Fine, I'll do it.
On one condition.

39:40.290 --> 39:43.772
What?Finish the song.

39:43.816 --> 39:45.208
Well, fine.

39:45.252 --> 39:46.601
You take the harmonies.
Uh.

39:46.645 --> 39:53.869
♪ I've forgotten you
just like I should ♪

39:53.913 --> 39:58.178
:
♪ What a guy

39:58.221 --> 40:02.182
♪ What a fool am I

40:02.225 --> 40:05.446
♪ To think my breaking heart

40:05.490 --> 40:10.059
♪ Could kid the moon

40:10.103 --> 40:15.238
♪ What's in store

