40:45.530 --> 40:47.749
I love them.

40:47.793 --> 40:50.230
Almost as much
as I love you.

40:50.273 --> 40:56.236
I love you, too, Sam.♪ For that would surely
break my heart in two... ♪

40:56.279 --> 41:00.283
But... I need to go
to back to Paraguay.

41:00.327 --> 41:02.416
Oh, please.
No, I can't.

41:02.460 --> 41:03.896
No, I know.

41:03.939 --> 41:06.594
I need to go alone.

41:06.638 --> 41:09.205
I need to figure out who I am

41:09.249 --> 41:12.426
before we spend the rest
of our lives together.

41:12.470 --> 41:13.993
No, I'll-I'll go with you.

41:14.036 --> 41:16.212
I'll find a way to
be happy there. I...

41:16.256 --> 41:18.606
Sam, that's why I love you.

